Package ohos.data.search.schema

Class PhotoItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
      • ohos.data.search.schema.Schema<PhotoItem>
        • ohos.data.search.schema.PhotoItem

  • public final class PhotoItem
extends Schema<PhotoItem>
    Represents the index schema for photo items.

    This schema is used to create indexes for photo items. It supports index fields size, height, width, photoCategory, shootingMode, shooting location (represented by country, province, city, district, road, latitude, and longitute), shootingDate, tag, feature, ocrText, holiday, and all the fields in CommonItem. Among these fields, identifier is mandatory and can be set via the CommonItem#setIdentifier(String) method.

    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
